data.description: Welcome to your new home in Greeley! This 4-bed, 2-bath has a new roof, gutters, heating, and central air systems for worry-free living.The home comes with the above the ground pool. The back yard also has a pear tree! Just 6 minutes from downtown Greeley, it's the perfect blend of convenience and serenity.No HOA! Come home to a place where every detail is designed for your utmost comfort and enjoyment. Your new beginning awaits in this Greeley gem!
